    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine, showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior boasts a flawless factory finish, enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a deep, glass-like luster\u2014completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' aroma; the premium leather seating remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the high-gloss trim pieces are devoid of scratches. Every electronic feature functions perfectly, and the mechanical components have been maintained beyond factory recommendations, documented in a comprehensive service history folder. Never driven in inclement weather and always hand-washed, the undercarriage is as immaculate as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that presents and performs exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
